@c ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@node rintl, math
@findex rintl
@subheading Syntax

@example
#include <math.h>

long double rintl(long double x);
@end example

@subheading Description

@code{rintl} rounds @var{x} to the nearest integer according to the
current rounding mode. It may possibly raise the inexact exception.

@subheading Return Value

@code{rintl} returns the rounded value of @var{x}.

@subheading Portability

@portability ansi, posix
